<http://www.example.org/rcao#encapsulates> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a V2X message to the AwarenessState(s) it carries." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#fusesState
<http://www.example.org/rcao#fusesState> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#fusesState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#used> .
