<http://www.example.org/rcao#fusesState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#fusesState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Explicitly identifies which awareness states were consumed during the fusion process." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#hasAwarenessState
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasAwarenessState> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
