<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasAwarenessState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://vcd.vicomtech.org/ontology/automotive#Object> .
<http://vcd.vicomtech.org/ontology/automotive#Object> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
