<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasAwarenessState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a subject (an agent-like object) to a state of awareness it possesses." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#hasResilience
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasResilience> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasResilience> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasResilience> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/rcao#ResilienceAttribute> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasResilience> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates an awareness state with its quality and trust metrics." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSourceResilience
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSourceResilience> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
