<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSourceResilience> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a sensor/source to intrinsic quality attributes (e.g., occlusion map) independent of specific measurements." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSubject
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSubject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSubject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSubject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://vcd.vicomtech.org/ontology/automotive#Object> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#hasSubject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Identifies the agent holding the awareness state." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#informs
<http://www.example.org/rcao#informs> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#informs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#informs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#informs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Models the flow of information from perception to comprehension." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#isAwarenessOf
<http://www.example.org/rcao#isAwarenessOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#isAwarenessOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/rcao#AwarenessState> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#isAwarenessOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#isAwarenessOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an awareness state to the entity (Object, Action, or Context) it is about." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#justifiedBy
<http://www.example.org/rcao#justifiedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
