<http://www.example.org/rcao#runsProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#runsProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<http://www.example.org/rcao#runsProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links the ADS or Algorithm to the computational process it is executing." .
# 
# http://www.example.org/rcao#usesSource
<http://www.example.org/rcao#usesSource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
